caption:
Our hearts go out to everyone affected by the devastating LA fires ⁠
⁠
To support those in need, we are donating to Vector Apparel Projects and Good Carma.⁠
⁠
If you’re looking for ways to help, visit Good Day LA’s website, which features a list of places where you can donate.⁠
⁠
Every effort counts. Stay strong, LA. ❤️⁠
